{"tid":1233812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"分析：今次200+1後 政府方面的壓力","createTime":"2019-06-16T22:19:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T23:59:23.000Z","uid":37504,"like":3,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6f3f90a1b016be09fec85ef580dfe3852f104688","tid":1233812,"uid":37504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T22:19:54.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟不才，以下是個人發夢夢到。<br />\n<br />\n6/9 - 反修例<br />\n- 103萬人 （哂馬）<br />\n當晚政府公開二讀繼續，唔比面哂馬<br />\n<br />\n12/6 - 叫政府撤回<br />\n- 4萬義士  （行動）<br />\n政府暫緩15/6<br />\n<br />\n16/9 - 放人，撤回，收回暴動<br />\n- 200+1   （哂馬）<br />\n<br />\n小弟覺得，而家義士可以先休息一下，政府會以上一次推斷示威者模式。其實而家驚到仆街，因為照咁睇，佢再唔應承示威者要求，下一次就係最少8萬人衝突。但又唔知你地幾時先郁手。淨係知道，示威者每次幾多人哂完馬，下一次就會有更多義士出行動（仲一直升級。）<br />\n<br />\n所以小弟應為今晚義士真係可以休息一下，等政府回應左先。<br />\n<br />\n然後發夢夢到政府如果唔妥協，先再FF升唔升級，同埋按比例升級？"},{"pid":"058ab4bde74d3ed9c40dfdbbff84c2567c23d411","tid":1233812,"uid":17510,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T22:35:17.000Z","msg":"休咩息姐<br />\n<br />\n目標仍未達到，同志仍需努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無真普選，不散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依個post由得佢沉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4861ddc6ca7cc6fab0aac5829ab67ee130d3bd74","tid":1233812,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T22:38:30.000Z","msg":"政府驚條撚咩<br />\n唔理你地 幾日後d人就散水啦"},{"pid":"39362f5e9271daa677cf12a7cd109ce0923546e8","tid":1233812,"uid":129340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4861ddc6ca7cc6fab0aac5829ab67ee130d3bd74","tid":1233812,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T22:38:30.000Z","msg":"政府驚條撚咩<br />\n唔理你地 幾日後d人就散水啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T22:40:20.000Z","msg":"所以先要deadline+ 升級"},{"pid":"3902e345a4a62d80fec994b92174